title: Theoi The Sky People Saga
description: My name is Wray Sky and I’m fourteen – again.This is the part of my story where I go back to the past, waking up on my second fourteenth birthday.The good thing is that I have a chance to fix horrible things that happened the last time I was fourteen. The bad things? Well, I have a boyfriend I don’t remember, I meet gods that I never believed in and I find out that my biological mother isn’t exactly human.
author: Lexus Luke
